<p><b><a href="https://archiveofourown.org/works/17570315">Ticket To L.A.</a> by Tomlinsontoes  |  nr  | 1601</b><br>Fun little airport fic based on the song "Ticket to L.A." by Brett Young.<br>Harry is a musician who meets Louis in an airport when all of the flights are delayed. After accidentally hitting him with his guitar case, Louis agrees to get a drink with Harry as long as he doesn't start playing "Wonderwall"</p><p>
<p><b><a href="https://archiveofourown.org/works/18380663">I’ll be there on the double, just send for me</a> by upwherewebelong  |  nr  | 1824</b><br>Inspired on this great twitter story:<br>“My flight was delayed 3 hours so I was doing what any human does when they’re bored. Minding my own business swiping through tinder & the guy behind me goes “ouch hard no for that one?” And I turn around ONLY TO SEE THE MAN I JUST SWIPED NO ON BEHIND ME HAHAHA” @taylor_stag<br>—<br>Title by one of my favourite tunes “Ain’t no mountain high enough”</p><p>
<p><b><a href="https://archiveofourown.org/works/71317201">Here’s to Us</a> by disgruntledkittenface  |  nr  | 2072</b><br>It was supposed to be a cozy Christmas in his partner’s small hometown. Instead, Harry gets dumped. When he gets snowed in at the airport, he’s just looking for a place to sit down.<br>But then he meets Niall.</p><p>
<p><b><a href="https://archiveofourown.org/works/50100334">Love Is In The Air</a> by justahappycloud  |  G  | 3758</b><br>When Louis gets stuck in an airport during a snow storm, he mentally prepared for his already bad day to turn into something even worse.<br>What he wasn't counting on was a certain green-eyed boy who would come to light candles in the dark of his bad mood.</p><p>
<p><b><a href="https://archiveofourown.org/works/5446847">it's not the end, i'll see your face again</a> by biolougy  |  T  | 4709</b><br>“What the fuck, mate?” Louis snaps as he rubs on the spot where his head had collided with the stranger.<br>“Maybe next time, you should know that you’re not 10 and running through the airport makes you look like a lunatic.” The stranger says, already up on his feet.<br>“You want help or what?”<br>Putting his thoughts aside, Louis looks up to see the stranger’s face and the large hand he is offering Louis to touch.<br>Goddammit, his luck just gets even worse.<br>or an au where louis and harry meet at an airport in new york city to catch their flight in time for christmas.</p><p>
<p><b><a href="https://archiveofourown.org/works/8972560">Makeshift Christmas</a>  |  G  | 5552</b><br>Everyone knows Christmas Eve is one of the worst days of the year to be at an airport. Louis didn't care about that fact too much when he booked a trip home to see his family for the holidays. What he wasn't expecting was the hours of delay caused by a snow storm, or to meet someone to keep him company.</p><p>
<p><b><a href="https://archiveofourown.org/works/4259433">could we ever feel much finer?</a> by slowtwilights  |  M  | 5898</b><br>“Sirs, I apologize, but I have some bad news,” she begins and Louis braces for the worst, like their 24 karat gold butt plug being confiscated. “Due to the inclement weather, your flight has been delayed for approximately 3 hours, though that could change depending upon the weather patterns.”</p><p>
<p><b><a href="https://archiveofourown.org/works/7935988">Come Fly With Me</a> by jaerie  |  M  | 9655</b><br>Louis and Harry are university students that meet in an airport while trying visit home during a school break. Their first flight goes as planned but their connection leaves them time for some unexpected adventures.</p><p>
<p><b><a href="https://archiveofourown.org/works/78589971">I’ll catch you, darling</a> by StormyDrama28  |  E  | 15752</b><br><i>"What?" Louis asks, raising an eyebrow.</i><br><i>"I'm Harry."</i><br><i>Okay. That's not what Louis had planned for an answer. Harry. Nice name. Nice face. Nice eyes. Nice smile. Nice everything. Louis is doomed.</i><br>Or,<br>How an evening spent stuck in an airport can change the course of your life.</p><p>


